{"tid":1610463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨既然將埸運動冠名「港獨」，何不將佢成真？","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T19:21:45.000Z","uid":96501,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"54c9f456afbd549d4274063117746a5293342d63","tid":1610463,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:37:42.000Z","msg":"入嚟想屌我話唔應該講獨立嘅，<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你醒下啦！</span></span><br />\n成場運動反送中只係導火線，<br />\n背地裏嘅不公義，社會問題政治問題，<br />\n有邊樣野並唔係源於呢個政府，呢個政權？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你醒下啦！</span></span><br />\n其實大家都明知呢場運動唯一嘅出路就係推翻呢個政權，<br />\n何不就將佢實行？<br />\n五大訴求，係啊就當條八婆應承哂，跟住呢？<br />\n返工嘅繼續返工，放題繼續放題，去日本嘅繼續去日本，<br />\n直到2047？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你醒下啦！</span></span><br />\n你地都明白由6月9號開始香港已經返唔到轉頭，<br />\n共產黨都知道香港唔會再係以前可以「把玩」係手掌嘅香港。<br />\n既然係咁，<span style=\"color: red;\">why not a true revolution?</span><br />\n<br />\n你哋可以當我鳩噏，但今日之後，<br />\n無論勇武和理非嘅所有行動，<br />\n無論去圍狗局，唔知幾多萬人大遊行等等等等嘅新聞價值同國際注目都會越嚟越低，<br />\n最後返返去2014年。<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪真係想咁？<br />\n唔想嘅就<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該你同我醒下</span></span>"},{"pid":"383b47a6a665a1b69cec5fa43a4e9cdc25801cd4","tid":1610463,"uid":96501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" cl